title: Police - Media Releases 10/11/2015 Man Fatally Shot Saturday Night on Rambling Brook Road Identified ...
text: ( Source : City of Nashville , TN) 10 /11/ 2015 October 11 , 2015 FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE The man killed in an exchange of gunfire Saturday night in the 1000 block of Rambling Brook Road is identified as William Frazier Jr., 18, of Fall Drive .
